data.description: Welcome to the charming yet affordable 3 bedroom, 1 bath home. This home offers comfort and style. The newly renovated home is perfect for comfortable living. This home has a updated kitchen and formal dining area, it also has a carport. The home is fenced in for privacy. Perfect for he first time homebuyers seeking a move in ready home. This home is turn key ready. Located minutes from shopping. This home also features stainless steel appliances and includes washer and dryer, it also has updated laminate flooring and a fenced in back yard for the kids to play.
